'''Strip Willpower''' is a monster-only spell producing a beam that tries to afflict you with the [[scroll of vulnerability|vulnerability]] [[status effect]], lowering your [[willpower]]. Its enchantment power is 6 Ã— [[HD]], but it ignores your willpower 1 of every 3 times.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.26]], this spell was called '''Strip Resistance'''.
*This spell was added in [[0.13]].

